{"type":"message","id":"f44c0dc4","parentId":"8c01af24","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:49:34.662Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个方式不太对，ACP 客户端期望的是 JSON 格式的消息，而不是直接的命令行输入。让我尝试另一种方式。\n\n在 OpenClaw 中，MCP 工具应该是通过 agent 系统自动调用的。我作为当前会话的 agent，应该可以直接使用这些工具。\n\n让我尝试使用 sessions_spawn 创建一个子 agent 来执行这个任务，或者尝试使用其他方式。\n\n实际上，我意识到在当前会话中，我应该能够直接使用飞书插件提供的工具。但是这些工具是通过 MCP 协议提供的，我需要找到正确的调用方式。\n\n让我尝试使用 openclaw 的其他方式来调用 MCP 工具。也许我可以使用 mcporter 技能来帮助调用 MCP 工具。\n\n让我先停止当前运行的进程，然后尝试其他方式。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"这个方式不太对。让我换一种方式，使用 mcporter 技能来直接调用 MCP 工具：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_fc651b0244a7466699d2e523","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"marine-breeze"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_6d725acda46c47ad8f8071e4","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/mcporter/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":268,"cacheRead":23226,"cacheWrite":1508,"totalTokens":25008,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00007504,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000757}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774000168101}}
{"type":"message","id":"64b5c05e","parentId":"f44c0dc4","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:49:34.690Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_fc651b0244a7466699d2e523","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Termination requested for session marine-breeze."}],"details":{"status":"failed","name":"echo create-doc --title \"飞书...p/feishu_doc_test.md)\""},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774000174682}}
{"type":"message","id":"4ca73361","parentId":"64b5c05e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:49:34.697Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_6d725acda46c47ad8f8071e4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: mcporter\ndescription: Use the mcporter CLI to list, configure, auth, and call MCP servers/tools directly (HTTP or stdio), including ad-hoc servers, config edits, and CLI/type generation.\nhomepage: http://mcporter.dev\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"📦\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"mcporter\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"mcporter\",\n              \"bins\": [\"mcporter\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install mcporter (node)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# mcporter\n\nUse `mcporter` to work with MCP servers directly.\n\nQuick start\n\n- `mcporter list`\n- `mcporter list <server> --schema`\n- `mcporter call <server.tool> key=value`\n\nCall tools\n\n- Selector: `mcporter call linear.list_issues team=ENG limit:5`\n- Function syntax: `mcporter call \"linear.create_issue(title: \\\"Bug\\\")\"`\n- Full URL: `mcporter call https://api.example.com/mcp.fetch url:https://example.com`\n- Stdio: `mcporter call --stdio \"bun run ./server.ts\" scrape url=https://example.com`\n- JSON payload: `mcporter call <server.tool> --args '{\"limit\":5}'`\n\nAuth + config\n\n- OAuth: `mcporter auth <server | url> [--reset]`\n- Config: `mcporter config list|get|add|remove|import|login|logout`\n\nDaemon\n\n- `mcporter daemon start|status|stop|restart`\n\nCodegen\n\n- CLI: `mcporter generate-cli --server <name>` or `--command <url>`\n- Inspect: `mcporter inspect-cli <path> [--json]`\n- TS: `mcporter emit-ts <server> --mode client|types`\n\nNotes\n\n- Config default: `./config/mcporter.json` (override with `--config`).\n- Prefer `--output json` for machine-readable results.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774000174691}}
