{"type":"message","id":"0d92b1fb","parentId":"8c919afe","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:56:47.227Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户的全局代理是通过环境变量设置的（HTTP_PROXY 和 HTTPS_PROXY），而不是在 OpenClaw 配置文件中。我需要：\n1. 找出这些环境变量是在哪里设置的（可能是 .bashrc、.zshrc 或其他 shell 配置文件）\n2. 帮助用户取消全局代理设置\n3. 为 Brave Search 单独配置代理\n\nOpenClaw 的配置中，web.search.provider 是 \"brave\"，但没有单独的代理配置。我需要查看是否有其他方式为 web_search 配置代理，或者建议用户修改 shell 配置。\n\n让我先查找代理环境变量是在哪里设置的。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！你的全局代理是通过环境变量设置的（`HTTP_PROXY` 和 `HTTPS_PROXY`），不是在 OpenClaw 配置文件中。让我帮你：\n\n1. **找出代理设置位置**\n2. **取消全局代理**\n3. **为 Brave Search 单独配置代理**\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_a5c2611de4ab480896884878","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"HTTP_PROXY\\|HTTPS_PROXY\\|http_proxy\\|https_proxy\" ~/.bashrc ~/.zshrc ~/.profile ~/.bash_profile /etc/environment /etc/profile.d/*.sh 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":259,"cacheRead":39749,"cacheWrite":4066,"totalTokens":44080,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00007252,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00007318}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774000600884}}
