{"type":"message","id":"351c8c7e","parentId":"2fe2c102","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:57:06.544Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"代理设置不在系统配置文件中，可能是：\n1. 通过终端配置（如 .terminal 配置）\n2. 通过 gnome 设置\n3. 通过其他方式在会话启动时设置的\n\n让我帮助用户：\n1. 检查当前 shell 的环境变量来源\n2. 提供取消全局代理的方法\n3. 为 OpenClaw 的 Brave Search 单独配置代理\n\n我需要查看 OpenClaw 是否支持为 web_search 配置代理，或者提供一个包装脚本来设置代理。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"代理设置不在系统配置文件中，可能是通过终端或 GNOME 设置临时配置的。让我帮你解决这个问题：\n\n## 解决方案\n\n### 方案 1：在当前会话取消全局代理（临时）\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_d985b184ad564f209199309b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"unset HTTP_PROXY HTTPS_PROXY http_proxy https_proxy && env | grep -i proxy"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":192,"cacheRead":44094,"cacheWrite":530,"totalTokens":44822,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00005376,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00005442}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774000620618}}
