{"type":"message","id":"7eed6637","parentId":"5d1bcd47","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:01:56.125Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 已经重启了（18:00:21 启动），但日志显示有飞书权限错误（cardkit:card:write 权限未开通），这和 web_search 无关。\n\nweb_search 使用的是 Brave Search API，不是飞书 API。让我检查 .env 文件是否被正确读取，以及 Brave Search API 是否正常工作。\n\n可能的问题是：\n1. .env 文件没有被 Gateway 读取（Gateway 可能不读取 .env 文件）\n2. Brave Search API 的配置有问题\n3. 网络仍然有问题\n\n让我检查 OpenClaw 是如何读取 .env 文件的，或者尝试直接在命令中设置环境变量来测试 web_search。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Gateway 已重启，但日志显示的是飞书权限错误（和 web_search 无关）。让我直接测试 Brave Search 是否能用，并检查 .env 配置是否生效：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_3ce978793ed64fffa20722ea","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/.env | grep -i proxy"},"partialJson":"{\"command\": \"cat ~/.openclaw/.env | grep -i proxy\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_3a5e42302222431680235c9d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -sI --proxy http"},"partialJson":"{\"command\": \"curl -sI --proxy http"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":19641,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19641,"cost":{"input":0.00216051,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00216051}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1774000892151,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted."}}
