{"type":"message","id":"5d0b8b47","parentId":"fb047ddb","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:02:56.904Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 18:02:27 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-feishu] DM | ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b [msg:om_x100b54e5fffae8a4c31bbcec5335871]\nSystem: [2026-03-20 18:02:56 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-feishu] DM | ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b [msg:om_x100b54e5fa3a7880c30da4bfa6d02e9]\n\nNote: The previous agent run was aborted by the user. Resume carefully or ask for clarification.\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e5fa3a7880c30da4bfa6d02e9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 18:02 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\"\n}\n```\n\n不要重启了，我之前不是告诉你方法和原则了吗，有限通过代理访问web_search，如果返回失败，则调用multi-search-engine技能进行搜索，明白，请写到你的md文件中"}],"timestamp":1774000976901}}
{"type":"message","id":"50f7fa38","parentId":"5d0b8b47","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:11.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提醒我之前告诉过他一个方法和原则：优先通过代理访问 web_search，如果失败则调用 multi-search-engine 技能进行搜索。他想让我把这个策略写到我的 MD 文件中（应该是 workspace 的配置文件，如 TOOLS.md 或 MEMORY.md）。\n\n我需要：\n1. 确认理解这个策略\n2. 将这个策略记录到配置文件中（TOOLS.md 或 MEMORY.md）\n\n让我先查看 workspace 中有哪些 MD 文件可以记录这个配置。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 明白了！我不重启 Gateway 了。我现在将这个搜索策略记录到配置文件中：\n\n**搜索策略原则**：\n1. 优先使用 `web_search`（通过代理访问 Brave Search API）\n2. 如果 `web_search` 返回失败，则调用 `multi-search-engine` 技能进行搜索\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_38651b8c34dd4a8288330c39","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu/TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":216,"cacheRead":49881,"cacheWrite":729,"totalTokens":50832,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000060480000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00006114}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774000976903}}
{"type":"message","id":"356dcc81","parentId":"50f7fa38","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:11.078Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_38651b8c34dd4a8288330c39","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\nSkills define _how_ tools work. This file is for _your_ specifics — the stuff that's unique to your setup.\n\n## What Goes Here\n\nThings like:\n\n- Camera names and locations\n- SSH hosts and aliases\n- Preferred voices for TTS\n- Speaker/room names\n- Device nicknames\n- Anything environment-specific\n\n## Examples\n\n```markdown\n### Cameras\n\n- living-room → Main area, 180° wide angle\n- front-door → Entrance, motion-triggered\n\n### SSH\n\n- home-server → 192.168.1.100, user: admin\n\n### TTS\n\n- Preferred voice: \"Nova\" (warm, slightly British)\n- Default speaker: Kitchen HomePod\n```\n\n## Why Separate?\n\nSkills are shared. Your setup is yours. Keeping them apart means you can update skills without losing your notes, and share skills without leaking your infrastructure.\n\n---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774000991074}}
{"type":"message","id":"87182f2c","parentId":"356dcc81","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:20.767Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我把这个搜索策略记录到配置文件中。TOOLS.md 是一个好地方，因为这是记录本地特定配置的地方。让我添加这个搜索策略。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_a2e40ec0422544b38e9ba625","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu/TOOLS.md","oldText":"---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet.","newText":"---\n\nAdd whatever helps you do your job. This is your cheat sheet.\n\n## Web Search Strategy\n\n**优先使用代理访问，失败时降级到多引擎搜索**\n\n1. **优先**：调用 `web_search` 工具（通过代理访问 Brave Search API）\n2. **降级**：如果 `web_search` 返回 `fetch failed` 或其他错误，则调用 `multi-search-engine` 技能进行搜索\n\n```\nweb_search → 成功 → 返回结果\n         ↓ 失败\nmulti-search-engine → 备用搜索结果\n```\n\n**代理配置**：\n- HTTP_PROXY/HTTPS_PROXY: `http://127.0.0.1:7897`（已在 .env 中配置）\n- 仅用于 web_search，其他请求不使用代理"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":286,"cacheRead":50610,"cacheWrite":449,"totalTokens":51351,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00008008,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00008074}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774000991079}}
