{"type":"message","id":"e09287b3","parentId":"671e3695","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:36.072Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_f96ceddc7920492a8b45f92f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-avatar/skills/multi-search-engine\n/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu/skills/multi-search-engine\n/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-embodied_ai/skills/multi-search-engine\n/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-openclaw_ai/skills/multi-search-engine\n/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multi-search-engine"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":308,"aggregated":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-avatar/skills/multi-search-engine\n/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu/skills/multi-search-engine\n/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-embodied_ai/skills/multi-search-engine\n/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-openclaw_ai/skills/multi-search-engine\n/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multi-search-engine","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774001016065}}
{"type":"message","id":"9401c2e9","parentId":"e09287b3","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:38.984Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了！在当前 workspace 中已经有 `multi-search-engine` 技能。让我查看这个技能的使用方法：\n找到了！让我查看这个技能的使用方法：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_75360baf77704499b6415982","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu/skills/multi-search-engine/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":83,"cacheRead":51383,"cacheWrite":463,"totalTokens":51935,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00002324,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000239}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774001016074}}
{"type":"message","id":"74b7daea","parentId":"9401c2e9","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:39.004Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_75360baf77704499b6415982","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\ndescription: \"Multi search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\"\n---\n\n# Multi Search Engine v2.0.1\n\nIntegration of 17 search engines for web crawling without API keys.\n\n## Search Engines\n\n### Domestic (8)\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\n\n### International (9)\n- **Google**: `https://www.google.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Google HK**: `https://www.google.com.hk/search?q={keyword}`\n- **DuckDuckGo**: `https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q={keyword}`\n- **Yahoo**: `https://search.yahoo.com/search?p={keyword}`\n- **Startpage**: `https://www.startpage.com/sp/search?query={keyword}`\n- **Brave**: `https://search.brave.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Qwant**: `https://www.qwant.com/?q={keyword}`\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\n\n## Quick Examples\n\n```javascript\n// Basic search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=python+tutorial\"})\n\n// Site-specific\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+react\"})\n\n// File type\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=machine+learning+filetype:pdf\"})\n\n// Time filter (past week)\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=ai+news&tbs=qdr:w\"})\n\n// Privacy search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=privacy+tools\"})\n\n// DuckDuckGo Bangs\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=!gh+tensorflow\"})\n\n// Knowledge calculation\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=100+USD+to+CNY\"})\n```\n\n## Advanced Operators\n\n| Operator | Example | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `site:` | `site:github.com python` | Search within site |\n| `filetype:` | `filetype:pdf report` | Specific file type |\n| `\"\"` | `\"machine learning\"` | Exact match |\n| `-` | `python -snake` | Exclude term |\n| `OR` | `cat OR dog` | Either term |\n\n## Time Filters\n\n| Parameter | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| `tbs=qdr:h` | Past hour |\n| `tbs=qdr:d` | Past day |\n| `tbs=qdr:w` | Past week |\n| `tbs=qdr:m` | Past month |\n| `tbs=qdr:y` | Past year |\n\n## Privacy Engines\n\n- **DuckDuckGo**: No tracking\n- **Startpage**: Google results + privacy\n- **Brave**: Independent index\n- **Qwant**: EU GDPR compliant\n\n## Bangs Shortcuts (DuckDuckGo)\n\n| Bang | Destination |\n|------|-------------|\n| `!g` | Google |\n| `!gh` | GitHub |\n| `!so` | Stack Overflow |\n| `!w` | Wikipedia |\n| `!yt` | YouTube |\n\n## WolframAlpha Queries\n\n- Math: `integrate x^2 dx`\n- Conversion: `100 USD to CNY`\n- Stocks: `AAPL stock`\n- Weather: `weather in Beijing`\n\n## Documentation\n\n- `references/advanced-search.md` - Domestic search guide\n- `references/international-search.md` - International search guide\n- `CHANGELOG.md` - Version history\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774001018994}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c015d6c","parentId":"74b7daea","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:48.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我了解了 multi-search-engine 技能的使用方法。它通过 web_fetch 调用各个搜索引擎的搜索页面来获取结果。\n\n根据技能文档，我可以使用 Google、Bing、Baidu 等搜索引擎来搜索\"飞书开放平台 发布文档 API\"相关内容。\n\n让我使用 Google 或 Bing 来搜索，因为它们通常能提供更准确的技术文档结果。我会构造一个搜索 URL 并使用 web_fetch 来获取结果。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的，现在我使用 `multi-search-engine` 技能来搜索。我会使用 Google 搜索飞书发布文档的最新信息：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_1bbb42d4da434412ae79c90c","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"maxChars":5000,"url":"https://www.google.com/search?q=飞书开放平台+发布文档+API+2025+2026"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":43872,"output":187,"cacheRead":9112,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53171,"cost":{"input":0.00482592,"output":0.00005236000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0048782800000000005}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774001019006}}
