{"type":"message","id":"da792e4b","parentId":"1dcbc96f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:16:32.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我有飞书应用的 appId 和 appSecret。现在我可以使用飞书 Open API 来获取 tenant_access_token，然后创建文档。\n\n飞书 API 流程：\n1. 使用 appId 和 appSecret 获取 tenant_access_token\n2. 使用 tenant_access_token 调用创建文档的 API\n\n飞书文档创建 API 端点：\n- 获取 token: POST https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\n- 创建文档: POST https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents\n\n让我先获取 tenant_access_token，然后创建文档。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我有飞书应用凭证了。让我使用飞书 Open API 直接创建文档：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_3ebf63e6b99d42f3a52fe56e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 第一步：获取 tenant_access_token\nTOKEN_RESPONSE=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"app_id\": \"cli_a93202000f399bde\",\n    \"app_secret\": \"twBum1qUuK99IibwhaDho0YtXgBgxca5\"\n  }')\n\necho \"Token response: $TOKEN_RESPONSE\"\n\n# 提取 token\nTENANT_TOKEN=$(echo \"$TOKEN_RESPONSE\" | grep -o '\"tenant_access_token\":\"[^\"]*\"' | cut -d'\"' -f4)\necho \"Tenant token: $TENANT_TOKEN\"\n\n# 保存 token 供下一步使用\necho \"$TENANT_TOKEN\" > /tmp/feishu_token.txt","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":396,"cacheRead":61218,"cacheWrite":163,"totalTokens":61783,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00011088000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00011154}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774001780118}}
{"type":"message","id":"2918701c","parentId":"da792e4b","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:16:32.273Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_3ebf63e6b99d42f3a52fe56e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Token response: {\"code\":0,\"expire\":2275,\"msg\":\"ok\",\"tenant_access_token\":\"t-g1043kgS7SFAYXVRB3BGPRYPO6XOX5LGDUZKW7OO\"}\nTenant token: t-g1043kgS7SFAYXVRB3BGPRYPO6XOX5LGDUZKW7OO"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":208,"aggregated":"Token response: {\"code\":0,\"expire\":2275,\"msg\":\"ok\",\"tenant_access_token\":\"t-g1043kgS7SFAYXVRB3BGPRYPO6XOX5LGDUZKW7OO\"}\nTenant token: t-g1043kgS7SFAYXVRB3BGPRYPO6XOX5LGDUZKW7OO","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774001792265}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a00391b","parentId":"2918701c","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:16:40.508Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我成功获取了 tenant_access_token！现在让我使用这个 token 调用飞书文档创建 API 来创建文档。\n\n飞书文档创建 API:\n- 端点：POST https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents\n- 需要 Header: Authorization: Bearer <tenant_access_token>\n- Body: {\"title\": \"文档标题\"}\n\n创建文档后，会返回 doc_id，然后需要使用内容编辑器 API 来添加内容。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"太好了！获取到 token 了！现在创建文档并添加内容：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_5fed8699c83f4d899cf72dad","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TENANT_TOKEN=$(cat /tmp/feishu_token.txt)\n\n# 第二步：创建文档\nCREATE_RESPONSE=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TENANT_TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"title\": \"飞书文档功能演示 - 2026年3月\"\n  }')\n\necho \"Create response: $CREATE_RESPONSE\"\n\n# 提取 doc_id\nDOC_ID=$(echo \"$CREATE_RESPONSE\" | grep -o '\"document_id\":\"[^\"]*\"' | cut -d'\"' -f4)\necho \"Document ID: $DOC_ID\"\n\n# 保存 doc_id\necho \"$DOC_ID\" > /tmp/feishu_doc_id.txt\n\n# 生成文档 URL\nDOC_URL=\"https://www.feishu.cn/docx/$DOC_ID\"\necho \"Document URL: $DOC_URL\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":378,"cacheRead":61381,"cacheWrite":496,"totalTokens":62261,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00010584,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0001065}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774001792277}}
{"type":"message","id":"7170b5c9","parentId":"1a00391b","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:16:40.745Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_5fed8699c83f4d899cf72dad","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Create response: {\"code\":99991672,\"msg\":\"Access denied. One of the following scopes is required: [docx:document, docx:document:create].应用尚未开通所需的应用身份权限：[docx:document, docx:document:create]，点击链接申请并开通任一权限即可：https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a93202000f399bde/auth?q=docx:document,docx:document:create&op_from=openapi&token_type=tenant\",\"error\":{\"message\":\"Refer to the documentation to fix the error: https://open.feishu.cn/document/uAjLw4CM/ugTN1YjL4UTN24CO1UjN/trouble-shooting/how-to-fix-the-99991672-error\",\"log_id\":\"20260320181640CF57CE5BF1D022190B5A\",\"troubleshooter\":\"排查建议查看(Troubleshooting suggestions): https://open.feishu.cn/search?from=openapi&log_id=20260320181640CF57CE5BF1D022190B5A&code=99991672&method_id=7055124481601732610\",\"permission_violations\":[{\"type\":\"action_scope_required\",\"subject\":\"docx:document\"},{\"type\":\"action_scope_required\",\"subject\":\"docx:document:create\"}]}}\nDocument ID: \nDocument URL: https://www.feishu.cn/docx/"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":212,"aggregated":"Create response: {\"code\":99991672,\"msg\":\"Access denied. One of the following scopes is required: [docx:document, docx:document:create].应用尚未开通所需的应用身份权限：[docx:document, docx:document:create]，点击链接申请并开通任一权限即可：https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a93202000f399bde/auth?q=docx:document,docx:document:create&op_from=openapi&token_type=tenant\",\"error\":{\"message\":\"Refer to the documentation to fix the error: https://open.feishu.cn/document/uAjLw4CM/ugTN1YjL4UTN24CO1UjN/trouble-shooting/how-to-fix-the-99991672-error\",\"log_id\":\"20260320181640CF57CE5BF1D022190B5A\",\"troubleshooter\":\"排查建议查看(Troubleshooting suggestions): https://open.feishu.cn/search?from=openapi&log_id=20260320181640CF57CE5BF1D022190B5A&code=99991672&method_id=7055124481601732610\",\"permission_violations\":[{\"type\":\"action_scope_required\",\"subject\":\"docx:document\"},{\"type\":\"action_scope_required\",\"subject\":\"docx:document:create\"}]}}\nDocument ID: \nDocument URL: https://www.feishu.cn/docx/","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774001800739}}
{"type":"message","id":"eb90ae79","parentId":"7170b5c9","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:17:01.936Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文档创建失败了，错误代码 99991672 表示应用缺少所需的权限（scopes）：`docx:document` 和 `docx:document:create`。\n\n飞书应用需要在开放平台申请并开通这些权限才能创建文档。我需要告诉用户这个情况，并提供解决方案。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"权限不足！飞书应用需要申请文档创建权限。让我告诉你如何解决：\n\n[[reply_to_current]] ❌ **权限不足** - 飞书应用需要申请文档创建权限\n\n**错误信息**：\n```\nAccess denied. One of the following scopes is required: [docx:document, docx:document:create]\n应用尚未开通所需的应用身份权限\n```\n\n**解决方案**：\n\n1. **打开权限申请链接**：\n   https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a93202000f399bde/auth?q=docx:document,docx:document:create&op_from=openapi&token_type=tenant\n\n2. **申请并开通以下权限**：\n   - `docx:document` - 文档读取权限\n   - `docx:document:create` - 文档创建权限\n\n3. **开通后告诉我**，我再帮你创建文档\n\n---\n\n**或者**，你也可以：\n- 在飞书开放平台控制台手动为应用添加「云文档」权限\n- 或使用你个人的飞书账号授权（需要 user_access_token）\n\n你需要我等你开通权限后再试，还是想尝试其他方式？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":325,"cacheRead":61877,"cacheWrite":755,"totalTokens":62963,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000091,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00009166}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774001800748}}
{"type":"message","id":"e62af937","parentId":"eb90ae79","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:19:11.622Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 18:19:11 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-feishu] DM | ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b [msg:om_x100b54e5bf281cb4c3e5a580678bb75]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e5bf281cb4c3e5a580678bb75\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 18:19 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\"\n}\n```\n\n开通了"}],"timestamp":1774001951617}}
{"type":"message","id":"3eeae558","parentId":"e62af937","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:19:32.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说已经开通了权限，现在我需要重新尝试使用飞书 API 创建文档。让我再次获取 tenant_access_token（因为之前的可能已过期），然后调用创建文档的 API。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好的！权限已开通，让我重新尝试创建文档：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_a9d3414a8c524b74a3e9a02e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 重新获取 token（之前的可能已过期）\nTOKEN_RESPONSE=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"app_id\": \"cli_a93202000f399bde\",\n    \"app_secret\": \"twBum1qUuK99IibwhaDho0YtXgBgxca5\"\n  }')\n\necho \"Token: $(echo $TOKEN_RESPONSE | grep -o '\"tenant_access_token\":\"[^\"]*\"' | cut -d'\"' -f4)\"\necho \"$TOKEN_RESPONSE\" | grep -o '\"tenant_access_token\":\"[^\"]*\"' | cut -d'\"' -f4 > /tmp/feishu_token.txt\n\n# 创建文档\nTENANT_TOKEN=$(cat /tmp/feishu_token.txt)\nCREATE_RESPONSE=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TENANT_TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"title\": \"飞书文档功能演示 - 2026年3月\"\n  }')\n\necho \"Create response: $CREATE_RESPONSE\"\n\n# 提取 doc_id\nDOC_ID=$(echo \"$CREATE_RESPONSE\" | grep -o '\"document_id\":\"[^\"]*\"' | cut -d'\"' -f4)\necho \"Document ID: $DOC_ID\"\necho \"$DOC_ID\" > /tmp/feishu_doc_id.txt\n\nif [ -n \"$DOC_ID\" ]; then\n  echo \"✅ 文档创建成功！\"\n  echo \"URL: https://www.feishu.cn/docx/$DOC_ID\"\nelse\n  echo \"❌ 文档创建失败\"\nfi","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":522,"cacheRead":60634,"cacheWrite":2694,"totalTokens":63856,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00014616,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00014682}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774001951621}}
{"type":"message","id":"459f370d","parentId":"3eeae558","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:19:34.278Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_a9d3414a8c524b74a3e9a02e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Token: t-g1043kgS7SFAYXVRB3BGPRYPO6XOX5LGDUZKW7OO\nCreate response: {\"code\":0,\"data\":{\"document\":{\"document_id\":\"WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd\",\"revision_id\":1,\"title\":\"飞书文档功能演示 - 2026年3月\"}},\"msg\":\"success\"}\nDocument ID: WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd\n✅ 文档创建成功！\nURL: https://www.feishu.cn/docx/WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1661,"aggregated":"Token: t-g1043kgS7SFAYXVRB3BGPRYPO6XOX5LGDUZKW7OO\nCreate response: {\"code\":0,\"data\":{\"document\":{\"document_id\":\"WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd\",\"revision_id\":1,\"title\":\"飞书文档功能演示 - 2026年3月\"}},\"msg\":\"success\"}\nDocument ID: WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd\n✅ 文档创建成功！\nURL: https://www.feishu.cn/docx/WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774001974259}}
{"type":"message","id":"59608163","parentId":"459f370d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:19:40.371Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太棒了！文档创建成功了！现在我需要往文档中添加内容。飞书 Docx API 使用 blocks 来添加内容。我需要使用以下 API：\n\n1. 首先获取文档的根 block ID\n2. 然后使用批量创建 blocks 的 API 来添加内容\n\n飞书 Docx API:\n- 获取文档结构：GET https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/{document_id}/rawcontent\n- 创建 blocks：POST https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/{document_id}/blocks\n\n让我先获取文档的根 block，然后添加内容。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🎉 **文档创建成功！**\n\n- **文档 ID**: `WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd`\n- **文档 URL**: https://www.feishu.cn/docx/WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd\n\n现在让我往文档中添加丰富的内容（表格、Callout、Mermaid 图表等）：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_89c86e6a032e41eeac6a9340","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TENANT_TOKEN=$(cat /tmp/feishu_token.txt)\nDOC_ID=$(cat /tmp/feishu_doc_id.txt)\n\n# 获取文档根 block\nRAW_RESPONSE=$(curl -s -X GET \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/$DOC_ID/rawcontent\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TENANT_TOKEN\")\n\necho \"Raw content: $RAW_RESPONSE\"\n\n# 提取根 block ID\nROOT_BLOCK_ID=$(echo \"$RAW_RESPONSE\" | grep -o '\"document_id\":\"[^\"]*\"' | cut -d'\"' -f4)\necho \"Root block: $ROOT_BLOCK_ID\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":410,"cacheRead":63328,"cacheWrite":688,"totalTokens":64432,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00011480000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00011546000000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774001974281}}
