{"type":"message","id":"aaa186e6","parentId":"b131d529","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:19:49.859Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"返回 404，可能是 API 端点不对。让我尝试使用正确的飞书 Docx API 端点来添加内容。飞书的 Docx API 可能有不同的版本或端点格式。\nAPI 返回 404，让我尝试正确的 API 端点：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_21147595ecac48e1b7cda3a5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TENANT_TOKEN=$(cat /tmp/feishu_token.txt)\nDOC_ID=$(cat /tmp/feishu_doc_id.txt)\n\n# 尝试使用 blocks API 添加内容\n# 飞书 Docx API v1 - 在文档末尾添加 blocks\nBLOCKS_RESPONSE=$(curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/$DOC_ID/blocks\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TENANT_TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"parent_block_id\": \"'\"$DOC_ID\"'\",\n    \"after_block_id\": \"\",\n    \"blocks\": [\n      {\n        \"block_type\": 1,\n        \"heading1\": {\n          \"elements\": [\n            {\n              \"text_run\": {\n                \"content\": \"📌 核心概念\"\n              }\n            }\n          ]\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"block_type\": 2,\n        \"text\": {\n          \"elements\": [\n            {\n              \"text_run\": {\n                \"content\": \"这是一个完整的飞书文档创建演示，展示多种块类型和样式。\"\n              }\n            }\n          ]\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }')\n\necho \"Blocks response: $BLOCKS_RESPONSE\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":403,"cacheRead":64016,"cacheWrite":437,"totalTokens":64862,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00011284000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00011350000000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774001980492}}
{"type":"message","id":"f9e0d748","parentId":"aaa186e6","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:19:49.999Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_21147595ecac48e1b7cda3a5","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Blocks response: 404 page not found"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":102,"aggregated":"Blocks response: 404 page not found","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774001989971}}
{"type":"message","id":"0852693b","parentId":"f9e0d748","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:19:58.568Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"API 还是返回 404。让我尝试不同的 API 端点格式。飞书的 Docx API 可能有不同的路径。让我查找正确的 API 端点。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"API 端点可能不对。让我尝试飞书 Docx API 的正确格式：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_575d802046d94e46b5dd9c8f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TENANT_TOKEN=$(cat /tmp/feishu_token.txt)\nDOC_ID=$(cat /tmp/feishu_doc_id.txt)\n\n# 尝试另一种 API 格式 - 使用 document_id 作为 parent\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/$DOC_ID/blocks\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TENANT_TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"parent_block_id\": \"'\"$DOC_ID\"'\",\n    \"blocks\": [\n      {\n        \"block_type\": 1,\n        \"heading1\": {\n          \"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"飞书文档功能演示\"}}]\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }' | head -100\n\necho \"---\"\n\n# 或者尝试使用 api.feishu.cn 域名\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://api.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/$DOC_ID/blocks\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TENANT_TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"parent_block_id\": \"'\"$DOC_ID\"'\",\n    \"blocks\": [\n      {\n        \"block_type\": 1,\n        \"heading1\": {\n          \"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"飞书文档功能演示\"}}]\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }' | head -100","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":437,"cacheRead":64453,"cacheWrite":427,"totalTokens":65323,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00012236000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00012302000000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774001990005}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac279016","parentId":"0852693b","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:19:58.904Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_575d802046d94e46b5dd9c8f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"404 page not found---\n<html>\r\n<head><title>404 Not Found</title></head>\r\n<body>\r\n<center><h1>404 Not Found</h1></center>\r\n<hr><center>TLB</center>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":296,"aggregated":"404 page not found---\n<html>\r\n<head><title>404 Not Found</title></head>\r\n<body>\r\n<center><h1>404 Not Found</h1></center>\r\n<hr><center>TLB</center>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774001998895}}
{"type":"message","id":"20f4f191","parentId":"ac279016","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:20:03.561Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"两个域名都返回 404。让我尝试飞书 Docx API 的其他端点格式。可能是 API 版本或路径的问题。让我尝试使用 v2 版本或者其他路径。让我尝试飞书 Docx API 的其他版本和路径：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_9ed3d49de27d47bca172fd70","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TENANT_TOKEN=$(cat /tmp/feishu_token.txt)\nDOC_ID=$(cat /tmp/feishu_doc_id.txt)\n\n# 尝试 v2 API\necho \"Trying v2 API...\"\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v2/documents/$DOC_ID/blocks\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TENANT_TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"parent_block_id\": \"'\"$DOC_ID\"'\", \"blocks\": []}' | head -50\n\necho \"---\"\n\n# 尝试使用 batch 端点\necho \"Trying batch endpoint...\"\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/$DOC_ID/batch\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TENANT_TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{}' | head -50\n\necho \"---\"\n\n# 尝试获取文档信息\necho \"Trying document info...\"\ncurl -s -X GET \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/$DOC_ID\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TENANT_TOKEN\" | head -50","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":373,"cacheRead":64880,"cacheWrite":513,"totalTokens":65772,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00010444000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00010510000000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774001998907}}
{"type":"message","id":"adbfe3d6","parentId":"20f4f191","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:20:04.066Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_9ed3d49de27d47bca172fd70","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trying v2 API...\n404 page not found---\nTrying batch endpoint...\n404 page not found---\nTrying document info...\n{\"code\":0,\"data\":{\"document\":{\"display_setting\":{\"show_authors\":true,\"show_comment_count\":false,\"show_create_time\":false,\"show_like_count\":false,\"show_pv\":false,\"show_related_matters\":false,\"show_uv\":false},\"document_id\":\"WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd\",\"revision_id\":1,\"title\":\"飞书文档功能演示 - 2026年3月\"}},\"msg\":\"success\"}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":482,"aggregated":"Trying v2 API...\n404 page not found---\nTrying batch endpoint...\n404 page not found---\nTrying document info...\n{\"code\":0,\"data\":{\"document\":{\"display_setting\":{\"show_authors\":true,\"show_comment_count\":false,\"show_create_time\":false,\"show_like_count\":false,\"show_pv\":false,\"show_related_matters\":false,\"show_uv\":false},\"document_id\":\"WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd\",\"revision_id\":1,\"title\":\"飞书文档功能演示 - 2026年3月\"}},\"msg\":\"success\"}","cwd":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-feishu"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774002004052}}
{"type":"message","id":"590198f6","parentId":"adbfe3d6","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:20:12.878Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"获取文档信息的 API 是有效的！说明 token 和文档 ID 都是正确的。但是 blocks API 返回 404。让我尝试查找飞书 Docx API 的正确端点来添加内容。\n\n可能是需要使用不同的 API 路径。让我尝试使用 `docx/v1/documents/{document_id}/content` 或者其他格式。获取文档信息成功！但 blocks API 返回 404。让我尝试正确的内容添加 API：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_7ed83440c59a41b6afd066c7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TENANT_TOKEN=$(cat /tmp/feishu_token.txt)\nDOC_ID=$(cat /tmp/feishu_doc_id.txt)\n\n# 尝试使用 content 端点\necho \"Trying content endpoint...\"\ncurl -s -X PUT \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/$DOC_ID/content\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TENANT_TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"content\": \"这是一个测试文档内容。\"\n  }' | head -50\n\necho \"---\"\n\n# 尝试使用 drive API 创建文件内容\necho \"Trying drive API...\"\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/drive/v1/files\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TENANT_TOKEN\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"parent_type\": \"folder\", \"title\": \"test\"}' | head -50","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":359,"cacheRead":65393,"cacheWrite":521,"totalTokens":66279,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00010052,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00010118}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774002004070}}
