{"type":"message","id":"b41655c9","parentId":"fe10f2ae","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:53:38.325Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要我安装一个可以操作他浏览器的技能。这涉及到几个问题：\n\n1. 首先，我需要检查是否有这样的技能 available（通过 clawhub 或本地技能）\n2. 其次，即使用户要求，我也需要考虑安全问题 - 操作用户浏览器是一个敏感操作\n3. 根据我的安全指导原则，我不应该获取超出必要范围的访问权限\n\n让我先搜索一下是否有这样的技能可用，然后向用户解释情况。\n\n用户可能想要的是类似浏览器自动化、屏幕共享、或远程控制的技能。让我先查看一下可用的技能。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 明白了！让我先查找是否有可以操作浏览器的技能：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_47dbdf231fd841b4b7e8f992","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub search browser 2>&1 | head -30"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_2fa05b9c53cc4be48eeae9a6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub search playwright 2>&1 | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4cdfd0b249db42688de9872c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub search puppeteer 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":260,"cacheRead":78891,"cacheWrite":780,"totalTokens":79937,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00007280000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00007346}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774004007431}}
