{"type":"message","id":"dd13421d","parentId":"44897929","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:08:59.983Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 18:55:40 GMT+8] Exec failed (clear-sl, signal SIGTERM) :: Not installed added 1 package in 1m\nSystem: [2026-03-20 19:03:08 GMT+8] Exec completed (sharp-fj, code 0) :: ersion of Playwright are installed Opening: https://www.feishu.cn/docx/WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd [32m✓[0m [1m飞书 - 登录[0m [2mhttps://accounts.feishu.cn/accounts/page/login?app_id=…\nSystem: [2026-03-20 19:04:52 GMT+8] Exec failed (tide-gul, signal SIGTERM) :: MB (30%) 61/174 MB (35%) 70/174 MB (40%) 78/174 MB (45%) 87/174 MB (50%) 96/174 MB (55%) 104/174 MB (60%) 113/174 MB (65%) 122/174 MB (70%) 130/174 MB (75%) 139/174 MB (80%) 148/1…\nSystem: [2026-03-20 19:08:59 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-feishu] DM | ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b [msg:om_x100b54e6e261d4a8c34f1bf2dc5a884]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6e261d4a8c34f1bf2dc5a884\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 19:08 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b\"\n}\n```\n\n登录啊，肯定，登录完，自动编辑飞书啊"}],"timestamp":1774004939977}}
{"type":"message","id":"acedcd5d","parentId":"dd13421d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:09:36.103Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说需要登录，然后自动编辑飞书文档。我需要用 agent-browser 来完成登录流程，然后填充文档内容。\n\n但是登录需要用户的账号密码，我不能直接获取用户的凭证。我需要：\n1. 让用户在浏览器中手动登录\n2. 或者用户提供凭证（但这样不安全）\n3. 或者使用已保存的登录状态\n\n让我先尝试点击\"切换至 Lark 登录\"链接，看看会跳转到什么页面。然后可能需要用户手动输入密码，或者我可以尝试使用其他方式。\n\n实际上，最安全的方式是让用户在自己的浏览器中登录飞书，然后我使用 agent-browser 的会话状态来操作。或者，我可以尝试使用 --headed 模式显示浏览器窗口，让用户看到操作过程。\n\n让我先尝试点击登录链接，看看会发生什么。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好的！让我使用 `agent-browser` 登录飞书并自动编辑文档。\n\n首先点击「切换至 Lark 登录」：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_d5cde9305cf0412d9d6d701d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 点击登录链接\nagent-browser click @e3 2>&1\nsleep 3\n\n# 获取新页面元素\nagent-browser snapshot -i 2>&1 | head -100","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":287,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":86374,"totalTokens":86667,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00008036000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00008102000000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774004939981}}
