{"type":"message","id":"d43e18f8","parentId":"40e7f2b8","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:10:07.952Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"浏览器启动失败，因为 Linux 的沙盒限制（AppArmor/userns）。我需要使用 `--no-sandbox` 参数来启动浏览器。让我添加这个参数重新启动。\nLinux 沙盒限制导致浏览器无法启动。让我使用 `--no-sandbox` 参数重新启动：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_ef14a79a8ab441c29ef6f7a2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 使用 --no-sandbox 参数启动浏览器（有头模式）\nDOC_URL=\"https://www.feishu.cn/docx/WyJgdbxKeoUMEExureDcR2Mjngd\"\n\n# 设置环境变量启用无沙盒模式\nexport PLAYWRIGHT_BROWSERS_PATH=0\nagent-browser open \"$DOC_URL\" --args \"--no-sandbox --disable-setuid-sandbox\" 2>&1 &\nsleep 5\n\n# 查看当前页面状态\nagent-browser snapshot -i 2>&1 | head -50","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":78909,"output":223,"cacheRead":9112,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88244,"cost":{"input":0.00867999,"output":0.00006244,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00874243}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774005002510}}
